pageTitle: City firefighters to the rescue | TheLancasterNews.com
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {21314=Nita Brown For the Lancaster News The Lancaster City Fire Department came to the rescue in a different way for YouthBuild and Habitat for Humanity of Lancaster County on Friday, June 1.
